    <item>
      <title>Diff your .spacemacs after upgrades</title>
      <link>/2015/09/01/diff-your-.spacemacs-after-upgrades/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Sep 2015 10:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2015/09/01/diff-your-.spacemacs-after-upgrades/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;When you upgrade Spacemacs, keep your dotfile in sync by using
&lt;code&gt;ediff-dotfile-and-template&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;code&gt;SPC f e D&lt;/code&gt;). This will enter an ediff session
with the .spacemacs template and your personal .spacemacs. Use &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;p&lt;/code&gt; to
move between regions and &lt;code&gt;a&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code&gt;b&lt;/code&gt; to copy changes from the template to your
.spacemacs. When you&amp;rsquo;re done, quit and save the changes with &lt;code&gt;q&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gfyitem&#34; data-title=true data-autoplay=true data-controls=true data-expand=true data-id=&#34;FaintSinfulBluewhale&#34; &gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;

